Jeremiah 20:8-9 

Hey, still over here in Jeremiah. 🙌🏻 Jeremiah is a prophet, called by God to deliver a message, that no one wants to hear. 🙃 He is STILL called to deliver, it regardless of who receives it. His calling is NOT in who receives it, 👉🏻 it is only in delivering it. So he’s feeling weary- understandably so. He is not seeing any tangible fruit, in delivering HIS message. He knows He is called but He doesn’t see the fruit. Do you ever feel this way? I sure do! This Christian life can feel weary, we are to be set apart, living unto the Lord, by HIS word. Jeremiah is in this hard place, he doesn’t want to keep going, he is about ready to give up. 

BUT GOD. His word is already in HIS  heart like a fire 🔥, a fire shut up in his bones. HE is weary of holding it in; indeed, He cannot.

God’s word is active + living + a
double edge sword. When we have it in our heart, it’s impossible to contain it. We indeed can not hold it back!! We need to spend time in the word, studying the word, saturating in the word, 👉🏻 so it gets into our hearts. May we get into the word + let it burn into our hearts, so when we are called - even if we are weary- we literally can NOT hold back. 🔥 

I’ve been praying this prayer all week: Lord, may your word be in my heart like a fire, a fire shut up in my bones. Even if I’m weary of holding it in; indeed, I cannot contain it! 🙏🏻🙏🏻";}i:82;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:83;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:0;}i:84;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEusUPDB_jf";}i:85;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:249:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/118784068_313448833297975_6147802718339431773_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_ohc=Cerjgzo3sfkAX_kuR4l&oh=51e9026afc099c851f7f32d8cb58ba13&oe=5F7C1D2E";}i:86;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:87;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:38960705758;}i:88;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:89;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:90;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:91;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391042873129108298";}i:92;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEusNMnlwNK";}i:93;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599254543;}i:94;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:77:"Our Slim Hydrangea case in our Dreamy collection! #topicsavi #hydrangea #pink";}i:95;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:96;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:3;}i:97;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEusNMnlwNK";}i:98;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:249:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/118765382_3072878146155131_816435496802750532_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_ohc=L-V4Zigxa34AX-gW9iz&oh=faa0be09095cc49a1beb62478a83932c&oe=5F7B0A3D";}i:99;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:100;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:39406881263;}i:101;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:102;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:103;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:104;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391042332332899232";}i:105;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEusFU9n7ug";}i:106;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599254479;}i:107;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:619:"TRUFAS DE OREO🤤
